<div id="sideL">
        <div id="tasks_label">
            <h2>TASKS</h2>
        </div>
    
        <div class="info">
            <div id="intro">
                <p>Click the + to enter new tasks. Before you start, be sure to click on the tasks you will be working on this session.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="task_list">
                <%= render partial: "form" %>
            </div>
        </div
    </div>
    
    <div id="main">
            <h1>Pomodoro Technique</h1>
            <p>The Pomodoro Technique is a time management method developed by Francesco Cirillo in the late 1980s. The technique uses a timer to break down work into intervals, traditionally 25 minutes in length, separated by short breaks.</p>
            <p><strong>When do you want to finish?</strong></p>
        
        
            <%= form_tag("/website", method: "post") do %>
                <%= text_field_tag(:hours) %>:<%= text_field_tag(:minutes) %><br/>
                <%= submit_tag("START WORKING") %>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    
    
